title: Presidential nomination sent to the Senate, 8-7-09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




August 07, 2009

 



Presidential nomination sent to the Senate, 8-7-09




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ______________________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                                                 August 7, 2009 NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:   Barry B. White, of Massachusetts, to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the United States of America to Norway.
